==English==

===Etymology===
From {{L.}} ''[[colloquium]]'', [[colloquy]]

===Adjective===
'''colloquial'''

# Of words, language, etc., used in [[spoken]] communication and [[informal]] written communication that reflects this usage
# Of or pertaining to a [[conversation]]; [[conversational]] or [[chatty]]
# Of informal language whose usage is [[localized]] to a particular area and not in general use. i.e. "I ain't gonna go o'er dere"

